Key Match Events: Jason Holder took 5 wickets in 2.5 overs
West Indies won the match by 17 runs
Jason Holder was named Player of the Match and Player of the Series
Post-Match Reflections: Jason Holder expressed pride in the team's performance and his role
Kieron Pollard discussed the team's resilience and the importance of rallying together
Miscellaneous Highlights: This was the 5th T20I of the series between West Indies and England
The series ended with West Indies winning 3-2
